title: The Walking Dead
description:
This collection was previously uploaded up to issue 45 by Seneca. Many thanks!

I&#039;ve added five issues to the collection and changed all the file names to the standard three-digit format (046, 047, 048, etc.) because most comic book reading programs I tested in didn&#039;t progress from issue to issue quite right. You would be reading issue #19, click Next to jump to the next archive, and it would jump to issue #2 instead of #20. Using the three-digit format, problem solved.

Plentiful kudos to the original scanners. Great job, people.

And, as always, if you like it, BUY IT. Support the artists.
